column2: SELECT G.objID, G.ra, G.dec, G.specObjID, G.type, Z.z, Z.zErr, SP.z, SP.zErr into mydb.sp_ph_radec2 From PhotoObjAll as G Join MyDB.MyTable AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.RA, m.dec, #) AS GN JOIN PhotoZ AS Z ON G.ObjID = Z.ObjID AND G.type = # JOIN SpecObjAll AS SP ON G.specObjID = SP.specObjID
